{"tid":1795521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地忽略左社會上一個族群","createTime":"2019-12-24T03:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T03:58:33.000Z","uid":344430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a98975a9e5ac1cda493457ea2097d5fb56cceee","tid":1795521,"uid":344430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"佢地叫清潔工人，除左人工已經比外判商剝削外，亦都夾住係警民之間，幫我地清走遺下既路障，又要冒住tg同二噁英維持街道清潔，但我地好少感謝佢地既付出；其實香港人欠左佢地好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我提議大家係聖誕節既時侯印d卡仔，一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">N95口罩，一支水，甚或給予一句鼓勵、道謝與道歉。</span></span>可能係佢地眼中唔算d咩，但代表住我地香港人從來都無忘記左佢地，佢地都係我地既一份子！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">we connect with基層！</span></span>大家點睇？"},{"pid":"c40aa2a6c527fc76ba236eabde15ecdeb3fd9406","tid":1795521,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:51:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bed5d2d5da3c294ff94be1874506261ddd0450c9","tid":1795521,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"贊成"},{"pid":"e0240e493130d53e74df4aced2057d15335ab467","tid":1795521,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"香港人人欠佢？<br />\n係香港欠左香港人 偷換概念 連基本都未搞清楚 負評"}]}